<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10106853>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–7. 1–4) Trichohippopsis birai, holotype female: 1) Dorsal habitus; 2) Ventral habitus; 3) Lateral habitus; 4) Head, frontal view; 5) Trichohippopsis exilis, paratype female, dorsal habitus; 6) Trichohippopsis magna, holotype female, dorsal habitus; 7) Trichohippopsis vestita, holotype female, dorsal habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10106853/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10106855>
    dc:description "Figs. 8–15. 8) Trichohippopsis suturalis, holotype female, dorsal habitus; 9–12) Trichohippopsis rufula: 9) Dorsal habitus, female from MZSP collection; 10) Holotype, lateral habitus; 11) Holotype, dorsal habitus; 12) Holotype drawing by Breuning (1958); 13) T. rufula sensu Breuning (1962); 14) Aprosopus buquetii, holotype, dorsal habitus; 15) Aprosopus gilmouri, holotype, dorsal habitus (true color changed due to the slide from which it was copied). Photographs in Figs. 10–11 by Camille Locatelli; photographs in Figs. 14–15 by Gérard L. Tavakilian." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10106855/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

